_sText:
Nav NOT INCLUDED YET.

Notes:

This is a Defuse type of map. The Terrorests are trying to blow
up the counter-terrorests base. There are thee targets they have
picked. The first one is the communications building (Bomb Site A),
that is located to the right side of the battle field from the Ts
spawning view. It has 3 satellite dishes on top of the building.
The second target is the CTs garage (Bomb Site B), which holds
there COOL transportation. This building is located to the left
side of the battle field, from the Ts spawning view. The final
target is the CTs base (Bomb Site C), This is located to the
right side of the battle field and all the way back. This is
from looking from the Ts spawning view.

Bug Fixes:
*None Needed Yet.
